<content type="application/x.deki0805+xml" title="menubar"><body xmlns:eval="http://mindtouch.com/2007/dekiscript"><div class="noinclude"><span class="script">template.XULRefElem()</span></div><p>A container that usually contains <span class="script">template.XULElem("menu")</span> elements. On the Macintosh, the menubar is displayed along the top of the screen, and all non-menu related elements inside the menubar will be ignored. To look native (at least on Windows), the menubar element needs to be placed inside a <span class="script">template.XULElem("toolbox")</span> element.</p><p>More information is available in the <a href="/en/XUL_Tutorial/Simple_Menu_Bars" title="en/XUL_Tutorial/Simple_Menu_Bars">XUL tutorial</a>.</p><dl><dt>Attributes</dt><dd><span class="script">template.PrefAnch("a-", "grippyhidden")</span>, <span class="script">template.PrefAnch("a-", "statusbar")</span></dd></dl><dl><dt>Properties</dt><dd><span class="script">template.PrefAnch("p-", "accessibleType")</span>, <span class="script">template.PrefAnch("p-", "statusbar")</span></dd></dl><h3 name="Examples">Examples</h3><div class="float-right"><img alt="Image:XUL_ref_menu.png" class="internal" src="/@api/deki/files/464/=XUL_ref_menu.png" /></div><pre>
&lt;menubar id="sample-menubar"&gt;
  &lt;menu id="action-menu" label="Action"&gt;
    &lt;menupopup id="action-popup"&gt;
      &lt;menuitem label="New"/&gt;
      &lt;menuitem label="Save" disabled="true"/&gt;
      &lt;menuitem label="Close"/&gt;
      &lt;menuseparator/&gt;
      &lt;menuitem label="Quit"/&gt;
    &lt;/menupopup&gt;
  &lt;/menu&gt;
  &lt;menu id="edit-menu" label="Edit"&gt;
    &lt;menupopup id="edit-popup"&gt;
      &lt;menuitem label="Undo"/&gt;
      &lt;menuitem label="Redo"/&gt;
    &lt;/menupopup&gt;
  &lt;/menu&gt;
&lt;/menubar&gt;
</pre><h3 name="Attributes">Attributes</h3><p><span class="script">template.XULAttrInherited()</span><span class="script">template.XULAttrInc("grippyhidden")</span><span class="script">template.XULAttrInc("statusbar")</span></p><h3 name="Properties">Properties</h3><p><span class="script">template.XULPropInc("accessibleType")</span><span class="script">template.XULPropInc("statusbar")</span><span class="script">template.XULPropInheritedWide()</span></p><h3 name="Methods">Methods</h3><p><span class="script">template.XULMethInheritedWide()</span></p><h3 name="Related">Related</h3><dl><dt>Elements</dt><dd><span class="script">template.XULElem("menu")</span>, <span class="script">template.XULElem("menuitem")</span>, <span class="script">template.XULElem("menulist")</span>, <span class="script">template.XULElem("menupopup")</span>, <span class="script">template.XULElem("menuseparator")</span></dd></dl><dl><dt>Interfaces</dt><dd><span class="script">interface("nsIAccessibleProvider")</span></dd></dl><p><span class="script">wiki.languages( { "fr": "fr/XUL/menubar", "ja": "ja/XUL/menubar", "pl": "pl/XUL/menubar" } )</span></p></body></content>